"","533","","LC","Yes","iii","VU","","VU","LC","LC","b","VU","bc","VU","","","","","b","VU","bc","Newport sites are under considerable development pressure, as are numerous other currently occupied brown field sites. Future habitat fragmentation is anticipated.","NT","cb","Continuing development pressure in the Thames corridor is reducing continuity of habitat, and the taxon does not seem to do well in fragmented habitat. Development is considered to have had a overall detrimental effect.","NT","","bc","LC","b","b","LC","LC","EN","<=5"
