"","580","","LC","Yes","iiiiiiivv","VU","Occupying all available habitat. Most sea-level dune systems used are vulnerable to a single Atlantic storm system. Climate change predictions tend to predict a higher intensity and frequency of Atlantic storm systems. These storms have significant potential to cause substantial damage to the existing population and available habitat.","EN","LC","LC","b","EN","bc","EN","","","","","b","LC","b","Occupying all available habitat. Most sea-level dune systems used are vulnerable to a single Atlantic storm system. Climate change predictions tend to predict a higher intensity and frequency of Atlantic storm systems. These storms have significant potential to cause substantial damage to the existing population and available habitat.Also a boreal taxon, which may respond negatively to climate change.","NT","bc","","LC","","bc","EN","b","b","DD","LC","VU","<=10"
