"","234","","VU","Yes","iiiiiiiv","EN","Significant habitat loss. Isle of Wight population cannot be refound. Welsh population is on unstable cliffs, where there is not a large enough population to maintain stability. Pastures above the nesting location cliffs are being improved, resulting in enrichment of area.","EN","VU","VU","b","EN","bc","LC","","","","","b","LC","b","Singular existing colony is at risk of localised storm surges. Pastures above the nesting location cliffs are being improved, resulting in enrichment of area.","NT","bc","","DD","","bc","LC","b","b","DD","LC","EN","<=5"
